The biomass was harvested by centrifugation at 3800 rpm for 20 min after cultivation, washed three times by BG-11 medium, and then dried in an oven at 50 °C for about 12 h. The dried pellet was weighed and considered as dry cell biomass (DCW). Biomass productivity (BP) was calculated using the following equation:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
